Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.77,0:00:14.67,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad you're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.67,0:00:15.82,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,This time, you won't get away.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.56,0:00:20.45,Default - italics,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Why is she here? It's still light out.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.45,0:00:24.16,Default - italics,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, if she hadn't been with me, \Nwould she have arrived this early?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.16,0:00:26.62,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,You never quit, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.62,0:00:29.00,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,I'm telling you, just give up already!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.00,0:00:31.60,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but this is something I cannot give up on.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.60,0:00:34.40,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,If you do as I say, I won't hurt you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.12,0:00:46.06,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,I have only one demand. Return my insignia.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.74,0:00:48.94,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,It's very important to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.62,0:00:58.70,Default,Rom,0000,0000,0000,,If she were just another magic \Nuser, I wouldn't back down,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.70,0:01:00.48,Default,Rom,0000,0000,0000,,but this one's trouble...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.48,0:01:01.87,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,What's with you, Old Man Rom?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.87,0:01:04.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Admitting defeat before we even fight?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.64,0:01:07.50,Default,Rom,0000,0000,0000,,Young lady, you're an elf, ain't ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.48,0:01:16.26,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Not exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.26,0:01:18.90,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,I'm only a half-elf.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.90,0:01:20.50,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,A half-elf?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.50,0:01:22.62,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,And with silver hair... Wait, are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.62,0:01:25.81,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,It's an accidental resemblance! \NReally, it's bothersome to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.48,0:01:30.00,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,You set me up, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.00,0:01:32.30,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? No, I didn't do anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.30,0:01:36.69,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,After you said you'd return it to its owner, \NI thought you were suspicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.69,0:01:40.20,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean? You two aren't working together?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.11,0:01:54.86,Default - italics,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Her nature never changes, no matter how \Nmany times I start over in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.72,0:01:59.17,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! What are you laughing about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.17,0:02:02.88,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, isn't that enough? Return her insignia.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.88,0:02:06.06,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,And, Sat— you, hurry and get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.06,0:02:07.98,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Try not to let anyone steal it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.98,0:02:10.47,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you suddenly being so nice?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.47,0:02:12.76,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,I don't understand at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.76,0:02:15.46,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,I don't understand you, either!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.46,0:02:17.15,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,What's up with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.48,0:02:19.82,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Puck! Shield her!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.22,0:02:27.83,Default,Puck,0000,0000,0000,,That was a bit closer than I expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.83,0:02:29.13,Default,Puck,0000,0000,0000,,You saved us!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.13,0:02:30.33,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Nice one, Puck!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.33,0:02:33.12,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness it was before five, \Nwhile you're still on duty.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.12,0:02:33.92,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.04,0:02:37.98,Default,Elsa,0000,0000,0000,,A spirit... That is a spirit, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.15,0:02:40.62,Default,Elsa,0000,0000,0000,,How wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.62,0:02:44.89,Default,Elsa,0000,0000,0000,,I have never dissected a spirit's stomach before.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.58,0:02:49.56,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.17,0:02:54.57,Default,Elsa,0000,0000,0000,,We can hardly negotiate, if the \Nitem's original owner is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.57,0:02:56.86,Default,Elsa,0000,0000,0000,,So I have changed my plans.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.86,0:02:59.57,Default,Elsa,0000,0000,0000,,I shall slaughter everyone here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.57,0:03:02.23,Default,Elsa,0000,0000,0000,,You failed to see your job through to the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.50,0:03:06.13,Default,Elsa,0000,0000,0000,,You talk a good game, but you do terrible work.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.13,0:03:08.41,Default,Elsa,0000,0000,0000,,You really are just another slum dweller.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.87,0:03:12.21,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,You bitch...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.48,0:03:13.98,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Cut the crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.98,0:03:16.80,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get your kicks from picking on a little kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.80,0:03:19.14,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,You guts-loving sadist!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.14,0:03:21.62,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Felt is doing her best to live strong...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.62,0:03:24.46,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Just because your plan was thrown off, \Nyou think it's over and flip tables?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.46,0:03:25.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you a little kid?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.57,0:03:27.11,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,You should value life more!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.11,0:03:29.48,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know how much having \Nyour belly cut open hurts?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.48,0:03:31.49,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I do!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.49,0:03:33.56,Default,Elsa,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.56,0:03:36.68,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in the process of letting the justice \Nand chivalry I never knew I had
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.68,0:03:38.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,denounce all the world's unfairness!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.91,0:03:42.13,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,And what I consider "unfair" is you, \Nthis situation, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.13,0:03:43.65,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Stay tuned, folks.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.65,0:03:44.49,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.77,0:03:46.81,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,All done buying time...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.81,0:03:48.56,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Get her, Puck!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.56,0:03:51.64,Default,Puck,0000,0000,0000,,A brilliant display of awkwardness, which I \Nhope survives through the ages.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.64,0:03:53.12,Default,Puck,0000,0000,0000,,I'd better live up to your expectations!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.12,0:03:56.63,Default,Puck,0000,0000,0000,,We haven't introduced ourselves, have we?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.85,0:03:58.40,Default,Puck,0000,0000,0000,,My name's Puck.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.40,0:03:59.94,Default,Puck,0000,0000,0000,,Remember my name
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.94,0:04:01.13,Default,Puck,0000,0000,0000,,after you die!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.78,0:04:06.87,Default,Rom,0000,0000,0000,,Did they get 'er?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.87,0:04:09.12,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Don't trigger that flag, old man!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.44,0:04:15.48,Default,Elsa,0000,0000,0000,,One should always be prepared.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.83,0:04:24.40,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Don't underestimate a user of the spiritual arts.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.15,0:04:31.02,Default,Puck,0000,0000,0000,,For a girl, you're well accustomed to battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.02,0:04:35.29,Default,Elsa,0000,0000,0000,,My, it's been a while since I was \Nregarded as a simple girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.29,0:04:39.08,Default,Puck,0000,0000,0000,,Well, from my perspective, all opponents \Nare basically babies.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.08,0:04:42.48,Default,Puck,0000,0000,0000,,Still, you're so strong, I almost pity you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.48,0:04:45.22,Default,Elsa,0000,0000,0000,,I'm deeply touched to be praised by a spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.25,0:04:52.12,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,If this turns into a battle of attrition, \Nwe should have a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.12,0:04:56.37,Default,Rom,0000,0000,0000,,No, fer a spirit, the real battle is how \Nlong they can stay corporeal.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.37,0:04:58.73,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, it must be almost five...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.16,0:05:02.48,Default,Elsa,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, and just when we were having \Nsuch fun. What a bore.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.48,0:05:04.87,Default,Puck,0000,0000,0000,,That's what sucks about being a ladies' man.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.87,0:05:07.24,Default,Puck,0000,0000,0000,,The girls just won't let you sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.62,0:05:13.08,Default,Puck,0000,0000,0000,,But you know, staying up late is bad for \Nyour skin, so we should wrap this up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.26,0:05:19.92,Default,Puck,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't just randomly throwing those around.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.40,0:05:22.09,Default,Elsa,0000,0000,0000,,Does this mean I've been had?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.36,0:05:23.94,Default,Puck,0000,0000,0000,,Goodnight!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.31,0:05:37.25,Default,Elsa,0000,0000,0000,,My, how lovely...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.49,0:05:40.72,Default,Elsa,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I was going to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.15,0:05:47.18,Default,Puck,0000,0000,0000,,But you're a girl, so I don't find that \Nsort of thing very impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.18,0:05:48.91,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Puck, can you keep going?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.91,0:05:51.44,Default,Puck,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I'm really sleepy...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.44,0:05:53.67,Default,Puck,0000,0000,0000,,I underestimated her a bit...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.67,0:05:55.40,Default,Puck,0000,0000,0000,,My mana's gone, so I have to disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.40,0:05:59.73,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take care of things here, \Nso you can rest. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.52,0:06:04.37,Default,Puck,0000,0000,0000,,If anything happens to you, I'll act \Naccording to my contract.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.37,0:06:08.68,Default,Puck,0000,0000,0000,,If it comes to it, call me, even if you \Nhave to squeeze me out of my odo.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.51,0:06:12.28,Default,Elsa,0000,0000,0000,,You're going away?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.40,0:06:22.15,Default,Elsa,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that is very unfortunate.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.64,0:06:40.12,Default,Rom,0000,0000,0000,,We can't keep just sitting around, watchin', Felt.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.12,0:06:42.08,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.08,0:06:45.44,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,If we're going to run, we should get moving now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.44,0:06:46.51,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,About before, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.57,0:06:49.25,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,I guess you kinda saved me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.70,0:06:52.31,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,But just a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.31,0:06:54.95,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,Also, don't call me a little kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.95,0:06:56.93,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fifteen, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.93,0:06:59.35,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,That can't be much younger than you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.35,0:07:01.93,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be eighteen this year...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.93,0:07:03.59,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,No way! You're totally a kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.59,0:07:05.73,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,You need to live a life that \Nshows on your face more!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.08,0:07:17.37,Default,Rom,0000,0000,0000,,Here I come!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.73,0:07:21.11,Default,Elsa,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, but isn't it a bit boorish to cut in on a dance?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.11,0:07:24.96,Default,Rom,0000,0000,0000,,If you wanna dance, I'll show you the \Nbest dancin' you've ever seen!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.84,0:07:31.88,Default,Rom,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go... Round an' round!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.99,0:07:40.89,Default,Rom,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? What in the—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.67,0:07:46.52,Default,Elsa,0000,0000,0000,,You're so strong, I was able to do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.52,0:07:47.44,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,Not gonna happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.13,0:07:53.48,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,Old Man Rom!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.22,0:07:58.62,Default,Elsa,0000,0000,0000,,You bad girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.74,0:08:02.96,Default,Elsa,0000,0000,0000,,You have neither the resolve nor strength to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.34,0:08:07.17,Default,Elsa,0000,0000,0000,,You should have at least stayed in the \Ncorner, making yourself small...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.17,0:08:10.48,Default - italics,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Damn, we're done for... \NThere's really nothing I can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.48,0:08:13.27,Default - italics,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I'll have to Return by Death and start over.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.14,0:08:19.69,Default - italics,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,No, I don't want to feel that pain again.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.17,0:08:22.01,Default - italics,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I don't wanna die...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.09,0:08:25.73,Default - italics,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I guess, as long as I have life,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.73,0:08:29.07,Default - italics,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,all I can do is fight with all my might.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.37,0:08:37.87,Default - italics,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Haidara!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.11,0:08:47.17,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.06,0:08:49.46,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.46,0:08:53.47,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Listen to me, Felt. I'm going to buy us time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.47,0:08:57.28,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give you an opening somehow. \NSo when I do, run as fast as you can!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.28,0:09:00.31,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,What? You're telling me to tuck my \Ntail between my legs and run?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.31,0:09:03.49,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Yes... Stick out your butt, \Ntuck in your tail, and run.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.49,0:09:05.73,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,You're fifteen, and I'm eighteen.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.73,0:09:08.76,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,That means you're probably \Nthe youngest one here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.76,0:09:12.12,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,So it's a given we'd pick the method \Nmost likely to keep you alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.12,0:09:12.82,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,It's a given!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.12,0:09:16.64,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,Give me a break. A minute ago, \Nyou were cowering in fear!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.64,0:09:18.66,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,That was then. This is now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.07,0:09:21.59,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not cowering now, so it's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.53,0:09:29.12,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.05,0:09:34.13,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Now! Go, Felt!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.01,0:09:38.66,Default,Elsa,0000,0000,0000,,You think I'll let her go?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.50,0:09:43.84,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, I'm awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.84,0:09:46.35,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,But that hurt the tips of my toes \Nmore than I expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.56,0:09:59.18,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,You let one get away...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.18,0:10:02.43,Default,Elsa,0000,0000,0000,,For once, I did feel a tiny bit annoyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.43,0:10:04.87,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Don't forget about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.38,0:10:10.91,Default,Elsa,0000,0000,0000,,I've grown quite tired of that game by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.91,0:10:13.29,Default,Elsa,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think you can still keep me amused?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.29,0:10:15.55,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,If you've got some hidden true power,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.84,0:10:18.32,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,now would be a good time to use it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.84,0:10:20.30,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,I do have a trump card.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.30,0:10:23.02,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,But if I use it, I'll be the only one left standing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.02,0:10:24.71,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,No exploding yourself, please...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.71,0:10:26.63,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Don't do anything hasty, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.63,0:10:28.20,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,I won't use it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.20,0:10:30.64,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Not when you're still here,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.03,0:10:33.50,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,doing your best.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.74,0:10:45.49,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Just now, I didn't see anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.49,0:10:46.21,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.21,0:10:49.36,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,None of that whole conversation ever happened!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.36,0:10:52.87,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I finally remembered why I'm here, to begin with.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.87,0:10:54.88,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I'll kill you, you shitbag!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.32,0:10:57.21,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you play your trump card!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.90,0:11:00.13,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I'll blow you away and get
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.81,0:11:04.77,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,a happy ending!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.52,0:11:08.74,Default,Elsa,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like you have a bit too much energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.18,0:11:10.67,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,You black widow!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.67,0:11:14.07,Default,Elsa,0000,0000,0000,,Well, there's no doubt you'll be \Nthe first caught in my web.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.61,0:11:18.32,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Nice cover!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.70,0:11:26.33,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch, damn it! How do you like this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.12,0:11:29.48,Default,Elsa,0000,0000,0000,,I caught you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.27,0:11:37.34,Default,Reinhard,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.68,0:11:51.85,Default,Reinhard,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like that was a close call,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.85,0:11:53.27,Default,Reinhard,0000,0000,0000,,but I'm glad I made it in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.32,0:11:55.48,Default,Reinhard,0000,0000,0000,,Now...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.71,0:11:56.90,Default,Elsa,0000,0000,0000,,You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.57,0:12:02.04,Default,Renhard,0000,0000,0000,,Shall we put an end to this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.15,0:12:07.49,Default - flashback,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,Someone!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.00,0:12:10.58,Default - flashback,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,Anyone! Is anyone here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.30,0:12:18.94,Default - flashback,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! Please... Please, someone...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.94,0:12:20.82,Default - flashback,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,Someone help!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.34,0:12:26.35,Default - flashback,Reinhard,0000,0000,0000,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.99,0:12:31.08,Default - flashback,Reinhard,0000,0000,0000,,I'll help.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.80,0:12:38.08,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Reinhard?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.51,0:12:40.08,Default,Reinhard,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, Subaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.08,0:12:42.28,Default,Reinhard,0000,0000,0000,,We meet again. Sorry I'm late.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.62,0:12:45.49,Default,Reinhard,0000,0000,0000,,Black hair, black clothes,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.49,0:12:48.09,Default,Reinhard,0000,0000,0000,,and a blade unique to the northern provinces.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.09,0:12:51.12,Default,Reinhard,0000,0000,0000,,There is no mistaking those characteristics.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.12,0:12:53.20,Default,Reinhard,0000,0000,0000,,You are the Bowel Hunter.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.20,0:12:56.40,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of evil nickname is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.40,0:13:00.07,Default,Reinhard,0000,0000,0000,,It was derived from her unique killing style.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.07,0:13:03.65,Default,Reinhard,0000,0000,0000,,Her name is known, even in the capital, \Nas that of a dangerous individual.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.65,0:13:07.71,Default,Elsa,0000,0000,0000,,Reinhard... Yes, a knight among knights,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.71,0:13:09.36,Default,Elsa,0000,0000,0000,,born to a line of master swordsmen, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.36,0:13:12.47,Default,Elsa,0000,0000,0000,,How remarkable, having all my \Nopponents be so much fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.26,0:13:15.36,Default,Reinhard,0000,0000,0000,,There are many things I'd like to ask you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.36,0:13:17.67,Default,Reinhard,0000,0000,0000,,I strongly suggest you surrender.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.67,0:13:23.77,Default,Elsa,0000,0000,0000,,You expect a starving predator to \Nresist such choice, juicy prey?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.86,0:13:27.20,Default,Reinhard,0000,0000,0000,,Subaru, stand back a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.20,0:13:29.20,Default,Reinhard,0000,0000,0000,,If you could stand next to her, I'd appreciate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.64,0:13:31.30,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,You got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.30,0:13:33.75,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,That woman is like a monster, \Nso don't lower your guard...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.08,0:13:35.93,Default,Reinhard,0000,0000,0000,,As luck would have it,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.93,0:13:38.96,Default,Reinhard,0000,0000,0000,,hunting monsters happens to be my specialty.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.48,0:13:45.52,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Old Man Rom is still alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.52,0:13:48.59,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,He isn't out of the woods yet. \NI have to heal him now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.11,0:13:53.27,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,You really want to? He's part of the \Ngang that stole your insignia.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.27,0:13:54.61,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,That's why.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.61,0:13:58.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I need him to recover, so he'll repay \Nthe favor by giving me information.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.73,0:14:01.92,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,He wouldn't lie to the one who saved his life.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.34,0:14:04.93,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,This is as much for my own sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.93,0:14:10.37,Default,Reinhard,0000,0000,0000,,I would rather not use violence on a woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.32,0:14:17.47,Default,Elsa,0000,0000,0000,,Just as the rumors say... No,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.47,0:14:20.79,Default,Elsa,0000,0000,0000,,you are even better.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.79,0:14:22.63,Default,Reinhard,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure I'll meet your expectations.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.92,0:14:25.60,Default,Elsa,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you going to use that sword at your hip?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.60,0:14:29.24,Default,Elsa,0000,0000,0000,,I would love to experience its legendary sharpness.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.24,0:14:32.64,Default,Reinhard,0000,0000,0000,,This sword can only be drawn when needed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.64,0:14:35.20,Default,Reinhard,0000,0000,0000,,The fact that it hasn't left its sheath
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.20,0:14:37.24,Default,Reinhard,0000,0000,0000,,means this is not one of those times.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.24,0:14:39.49,Default,Elsa,0000,0000,0000,,I do believe I've been underestimated.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.49,0:14:42.99,Default,Reinhard,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's an upsetting judgment for me, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.99,0:14:44.00,Default,Reinhard,0000,0000,0000,,Therefore,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.51,0:14:46.23,Default,Reinhard,0000,0000,0000,,I shall take you on with this instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.21,0:14:49.99,Default,Reinhard,0000,0000,0000,,Do you object?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.32,0:14:53.70,Default,Elsa,0000,0000,0000,,No, it is wonderful. Wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.70,0:14:55.12,Default,Elsa,0000,0000,0000,,Do entertain me, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.50,0:15:04.81,Default,Reinhard,0000,0000,0000,,If you've lost your weapon, \NI strongly suggest you surrender.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.20,0:15:08.58,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,She's got a second one, Reinhard!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.77,0:15:13.17,Default,Elsa,0000,0000,0000,,I'm impressed you knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.17,0:15:15.63,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I've personally experienced it...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.63,0:15:18.67,Default,Elsa,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't have merely two fangs.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.67,0:15:21.14,Default,Elsa,0000,0000,0000,,Would you mind if we start again?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.14,0:15:24.73,Default,Reinhard,0000,0000,0000,,If I divest you of all your weapons, \Nwill you be satisfied?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.73,0:15:26.69,Default,Elsa,0000,0000,0000,,If I lose my fangs, I'll use my claws.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.11,0:15:29.19,Default,Elsa,0000,0000,0000,,If I lose my claws, I'll use my bones.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.19,0:15:30.82,Default,Elsa,0000,0000,0000,,And if I lose my bones, I'll use my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.62,0:15:33.53,Default,Elsa,0000,0000,0000,,That is how a "Bowel Hunter" fights.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.31,0:15:39.75,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Surely Reinhard won't fail to land \Nthe decisive blow, will he?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.16,0:15:44.28,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Because I'm using my spiritual arts, \Nhe cannot fight at full strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.66,0:15:46.24,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,What do those have to do with each other?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.24,0:15:48.87,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,If Reinhard were truly intent on fighting,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.87,0:15:51.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,all the mana in the atmosphere \Nwould turn away from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.64,0:15:54.48,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,I'm almost done healing him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.48,0:15:56.64,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,When I give the signal, let him know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.45,0:16:04.40,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Now he's all right. Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.40,0:16:07.55,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Reinhard! I don't really get it, but do your thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.85,0:16:11.60,Default,Elsa,0000,0000,0000,,What will you show me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.06,0:16:13.91,Default,Reinhard,0000,0000,0000,,The swordplay of the Astrea family.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.68,0:16:24.08,Default,Elsa,0000,0000,0000,,The Bowel Hunter, Elsa Granhiert.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.87,0:16:28.97,Default,Reinhard,0000,0000,0000,,Reinhard van Astrea, of the \Nline of master swordsmen.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.16,0:16:52.94,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, whoa, whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.55,0:17:08.29,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Hunting monsters is your specialty, my ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.62,0:17:11.28,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,You're a monster yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.28,0:17:15.01,Default,Reinhard,0000,0000,0000,,Even I'm a bit hurt by a comment \Nlike that, Subaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.60,0:17:18.41,Default,Reinhard,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry I asked too much of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.88,0:17:20.10,Default,Reinhard,0000,0000,0000,,Rest well now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.89,0:17:23.69,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,There isn't a shadow left, let alone a body...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.69,0:17:26.30,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,This is all that's left after just a sword swing?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.30,0:17:27.76,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,It's over now?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.76,0:17:30.96,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, somehow or other. Literally.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.81,0:17:35.57,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you staring at me? That's quite rude.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.92,0:17:40.34,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,It's just, you still have your arms \Nand legs, even your head...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.34,0:17:43.95,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I do. Don't say such scary things.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.95,0:17:46.55,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you're right. It's obvious, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.55,0:17:48.19,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I still have my arms, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.19,0:17:52.05,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,And there's no knife in my back \Nor gaping hole in my gut.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.41,0:17:56.31,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,You talk as if you've experienced \Nthose things before.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.31,0:17:58.73,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,There was a time when I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.73,0:18:01.59,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah, Reinhard... I haven't thanked you yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.59,0:18:03.03,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,You saved my ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.03,0:18:04.75,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Back in the alley, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.75,0:18:07.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess you heard my heart's cries for help, friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.70,0:18:10.96,Default,Reinhard,0000,0000,0000,,If I did do that, I'd certainly be proud...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.96,0:18:12.09,Default,Reinhard,0000,0000,0000,,Friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.75,0:18:15.79,Default,Reinhard,0000,0000,0000,,She was desperately running around the streets,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.79,0:18:18.15,Default,Reinhard,0000,0000,0000,,and she asked for my help.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.71,0:18:20.10,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.10,0:18:21.75,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Now, hang on...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.75,0:18:25.72,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,If she hadn't brought Reinhard, \Nwe'd have been destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.72,0:18:29.87,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Just take a look at this face, and spare \Nme the ice-statue punishment, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.87,0:18:31.38,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't do anything so violent!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.77,0:18:33.88,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,And what does your face have to do with—
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.59,0:18:35.42,Default,Reinhard,0000,0000,0000,,Subaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.77,0:18:48.12,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,She'll go for the gut!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.65,0:18:52.18,Default,Elsa,0000,0000,0000,,He got in my way again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.18,0:18:53.31,Default,Reinhard,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough, Elsa!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.16,0:19:01.22,Default,Elsa,0000,0000,0000,,Soon enough, I'll disembowel everyone here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.28,0:19:06.91,Default,Elsa,0000,0000,0000,,Till then, take good care of your bowels.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.40,0:19:09.62,Default,Reinhard,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.44,0:19:13.33,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Whether I'm all right doesn't \Nmatter! More importantly,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.68,0:19:16.36,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,are you all right? That was far too reckless!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.06,0:19:15.24,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.77,0:19:18.73,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it was no problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.40,0:19:23.51,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I sure took the long road, but I \Nfinally reached this point.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.83,0:19:27.03,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Natsuki Subaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.03,0:19:30.94,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,And I just saved your life from a heinous villain!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.94,0:19:32.02,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Are we OK on that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.28,0:19:34.64,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,"OK"?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.64,0:19:36.96,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,It means "Are we clear on that?" So...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.96,0:19:38.58,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.58,0:19:40.34,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,O-OK...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.34,0:19:42.58,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,I, your rescuer, saved your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.58,0:19:44.95,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,And you are the heroine I saved!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.95,0:19:48.90,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,So wouldn't that mean you should \Nrepay me in kind? Wouldn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.90,0:19:50.51,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,All right, I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.51,0:19:53.81,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Only if it's within my power, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.81,0:19:57.63,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, I have only one request!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.97,0:20:00.34,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, my request is...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.90,0:20:08.10,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me your name.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.15,0:20:12.16,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Emilia.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.16,0:20:12.76,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.62,0:20:18.38,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Emilia. Just Emilia.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.83,0:20:23.28,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Subaru. For saving me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.54,0:20:30.62,Default - italics,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,All those times I got hurt, all the crying I did,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.62,0:20:35.21,Default - italics,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,all the pain I felt, all the fighting \NI did with my life at stake...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.21,0:20:38.64,Default - italics,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,And my reward was her name and a single smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.52,0:20:41.81,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.81,0:20:43.51,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Talk about unequal compensation.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.04,0:20:50.93,Default,Reinhard,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, Subaru, I'm impressed that you're unhurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.93,0:20:53.59,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,That thing protected me just in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.59,0:20:56.48,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,If not for that, I'd be in two pieces right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.48,0:20:58.78,Default,Reinhard,0000,0000,0000,,True, if not for this...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.47,0:21:00.18,Default,Reinhard,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.59,0:21:08.57,Default,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-oh. I should have seen this coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.56,0:21:10.57,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Subaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.41,0:21:12.45,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Subaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.70,0:21:16.82,Default - italics,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,Man...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.47,0:21:20.67,Default - italics,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,She's so cute when she's panicking...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.44,0:21:23.77,Default - italics,Subaru,0000,0000,0000,,A parallel world fantasy...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.34,0:21:29.52,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,There. His treatment is complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.52,0:21:31.41,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,He should be over the hump now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.41,0:21:35.96,Default,Reinhard,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, Lady Emilia, what is \Nyour relation to Subaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.51,0:21:38.70,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,A passing acquaintance?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.96,0:21:42.82,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,I don't recall ever meeting him before.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.82,0:21:46.24,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,I thought our meeting, earlier today, was the first.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.24,0:21:49.19,Default,Reinhard,0000,0000,0000,,But he was looking for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.19,0:21:51.26,Default,Reinhard,0000,0000,0000,,He said he had something to give you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.26,0:21:53.04,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,That's why it's so strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.66,0:21:55.90,Default,Reinhard,0000,0000,0000,,What shall we do with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.90,0:21:59.33,Default,Reinhard,0000,0000,0000,,I would be glad to take him home as a guest.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.33,0:22:02.27,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'll take him home with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.27,0:22:04.73,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,That way, I can learn what's really going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.30,0:22:09.85,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,But more importantly, what will become \Nof that girl and the old man?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.85,0:22:13.81,Default,Reinhard,0000,0000,0000,,Officially, I cannot overlook what they've done.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.29,0:22:15.39,Default,Reinhard,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.92,0:22:18.66,Default,Reinhard,0000,0000,0000,,Unfortunately, I'm off duty today.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.32,0:22:21.90,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,You're a bad knight.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.46,0:22:28.18,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Is this old man your family?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.93,0:22:33.44,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,Something like that. \NOld Man Rom is the only one I have...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.99,0:22:36.83,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,I guess he's like my grandpa.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.27,0:22:40.80,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,I see. I only have one family member, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.24,0:22:43.92,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,But he's always asleep at the \Nmost important moments.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.92,0:22:46.71,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,When he's awake, I'd never say that aloud.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.92,0:22:50.67,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you'd be a lot harsher to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.67,0:22:51.46,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.59,0:22:56.31,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,You saved my life, and I can't let a debt go unpaid.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.31,0:22:57.81,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,I'll return what I stole.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.72,0:23:02.22,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,If it's important, keep it hidden, \Nso no one can steal it again!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.22,0:23:05.90,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,It feels funny, having you give me that warning.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.23,0:23:11.53,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,Reinhard?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.98,0:23:13.66,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,You're hurting me! Let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.58,0:23:16.66,Default,Reinhard,0000,0000,0000,,How can this be?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.93,0:23:18.09,Default,Reinhard,0000,0000,0000,,What is your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.09,0:23:20.16,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? It's Felt...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.16,0:23:22.89,Default,Reinhard,0000,0000,0000,,And your family name? How old are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.89,0:23:26.09,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have anything fancy like a family name!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.09,0:23:28.93,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,I'm... about fifteen, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.93,0:23:30.53,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know my birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.53,0:23:31.99,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,Look, just let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.99,0:23:36.14,Default,Reinhard,0000,0000,0000,,Lady Emilia, I am afraid I cannot \Nkeep my promise to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.14,0:23:39.17,Default,Reinhard,0000,0000,0000,,I shall be taking this girl with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.17,0:23:43.42,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,May I ask why? If it's for stealing my insignia...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.42,0:23:45.61,Default,Reinhard,0000,0000,0000,,That is, indeed, no small crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.29,0:23:51.74,Default,Reinhard,0000,0000,0000,,But compared to the gravity of overlooking \Nthe crime unfolding before me, it's trivial.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.51,0:23:54.09,Default,Reinhard,0000,0000,0000,,I need you to come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.09,0:23:56.22,Default,Reinhard,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, but I cannot allow you to refuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.22,0:23:59.72,Default,Felt,0000,0000,0000,,Get over yourself! Just because you saved me—
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.25,0:24:03.85,Default,Emilia,0000,0000,0000,,That wasn't very courtly, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.85,0:24:05.84,Default,Reinhard,0000,0000,0000,,I was careful not to use too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.84,0:24:09.93,Default,Reinhard,0000,0000,0000,,Lady Emilia, I will be calling \Nupon you soon, most likely.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.80,0:24:11.84,Default,Reinhard,0000,0000,0000,,I hope you understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.48,0:24:16.41,Default,Reinhard,0000,0000,0000,,Please take good care of Subaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.31,0:24:28.24,Default,Reinhard,0000,0000,0000,,Today may be the last chance we \Nhave to gaze calmly at the moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.74,0:24:35.78,Episode Title,Title,0000,0000,0000,,Starting Life from Zero in {\c&H5A4CDD&}Another {\c&HFFFFFF&}World
